{"tid":671295,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子大元邨燒衫　手部灼傷送院","createTime":"2018-05-20T04:19:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-20T05:17:11.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"79bce73c4281b06cb0be2810a95989a04707aa57","tid":671295,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T04:19:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180520/photo/bkn-20180520110347898-0520_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180520114639\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180520%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180520110347898-0520_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180520114639&h=3d2600b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現場遺下燒過的衣服。(張世洋攝)<br />\n<br />\n大埔一名男子燒衫灼傷。今晨9時許，大元邨泰榮樓地下有一名男子在大叫大釀，驚動在場街坊，男子更突然脫去身上衣服，然後用打火機點火燒衫，街坊見狀立即報警。男子手部受傷，由救護車送院治理。警方到場正調查事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180520/bkn-20180520110347898-0520_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180520%2Fbkn-20180520110347898-0520_00822_001.html&d=z7vz%2BB42COkwiY3XNLusEL5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=3f511d8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180520/bkn-20180520110347898-0520_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"c77c1084ed0114c3146f4db4601c4f416de54dc6","tid":671295,"uid":142313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T04:29:07.000Z","msg":"傻人發現案"},{"pid":"4ebc62164ccc122d4f85846712c37b8a2425105c","tid":671295,"uid":165360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T05:17:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}